The paper deals with a communication channel with an adversarial jammer, which is a common topic in information theory (cs.IT) and computer security (cs.CR). The concept of writing on a dirty paper is also related to signal processing (cs.SI) and multimedia (cs.MM). Finally, the paper discusses the capacity of the channel, which is a fundamental concept in networking (cs.NI).
